snippet.title: AJTech
snippet.description: Hey I'm Ajay and I am 18 years old, on this channel I focus on game development with Unity 3D and C# and teaching you how to build games for yourself. My most recent series focuses on my development logs where I will build a game using Unity and show you the process from pre-production all the way to release. So what are you waiting for? Jump right in!
